==English==

===Noun===
'''challenge'''  (''plural:'' '''[[challenges]]''')
{{wikipediapar|Challenge}}
# An [[instigation]] or [[antagonization]] intended to convince a [[person]] to perform an [[action]] they otherwise would not.
# A [[difficult]] [[task]].

